org.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM spree_variants INNER JOIN spree_products ON spree_products.id = spree_variants.product_id WHERE spree_variants.deleted_at IS NULL AND (LOWER(spree_products.name) LIKE LOWER('%White dress%') OR LOWER(sku) LIKE LOWER('%White dress%'))

rewrites.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM spree_variants INNER JOIN spree_products ON spree_products.id = spree_variants.product_id WHERE spree_variants.deleted_at IS NULL AND (LOWER(spree_products.name) LIKE LOWER('%White dress%') OR LOWER(sku) LIKE LOWER('%White dress%')) LIMIT 1
